high_descs: Turn left, go straight to the desk fan and then go to the desk lamp on your right.
Pick up the strawberry lying on the left side of the desk lamp.
anns.task_desc: Put a strawberry in the light of a desk lamp.

high_descs: Turn left, move, take right, move towards the desk lamp.
Take the straw berry from the table.
anns.task_desc: To put the desk lamp on, take the straw berry from table.

high_descs: Turn left and turn right to the desk lamp.
Pick the straw berry from the desk.
anns.task_desc: Examine a straw berry  by the light of a desk lamp.
